      • setDistributedPort

        public EthernetTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setDistributedPort(String distributedPort)
        Key of the distributed virtual port that backs the virtual Ethernet adapter. This property will be null if the virtual Ethernet device is not bound to a distributed virtual port; this can happen if the virtual machine is powered off or the virtual Ethernet device is not connected.
        Parameters:
        distributedPort - New value for the property.

      • setConnectionCookie

        public EthernetTypes.BackingInfo.Builder setConnectionCookie(Long connectionCookie)
        Server-generated cookie that identifies the connection to the port. This ookie may be used to verify that the virtual machine is the rightful owner of the port. This property will be null if the virtual Ethernet device is not bound to a distributed virtual port; this can happen if the virtual machine is powered off or the virtual Ethernet device is not connected.
        Parameters:
        connectionCookie - New value for the property.
